Author: nazoka
Title: ⚡ [ANN] SENTIGRAPH.IO ⚡ ⭐ Improving Future Events Based on Emotion Data ⭐
Body: Thanks for the comments. We need a blockchain to ensure that the computation of the graph index (which is the value of the strength of the sentiments of a subscriber to a. given network) is publicly visible and transparent. The beneficiaries can trust that there has been no external manipulatioin of the data (not just in te data thereof), but in the computation of it in the first place.  Also, we want to leverage the "natural" benefits of blockchain such as continuius uptime, security and cost savings.

Author: nazoka
Title: ⚡ [ANN] SENTIGRAPH.IO ⚡ ⭐ Improving Future Events Based on Emotion Data ⭐
Body: Thanks for reaching out Sir. Please accept our apologies for the unusual  gap in communication. We have been busy with our milestones. One of which is completing our next iteration of our centralized prototype. The prototype computes the actual sentiments of events that are represented by twitter hashtags. We are seeking testers and feedback as well.  Prototype: http://dapp.sentigraph.io  Also we have been strengthening our brand and growing our Social Media community on Telegram/Reddit/Discord.  Finally we have partnered with Applicature.com to start the dapp and architecture for the EVP (The binary options aspect of our platform, though this needs to be licensed in certain jurisdictions). We also have improved our advisory board.  Along side all these, our Private Sale is on as announced https://medium.com/sentigraph-io/the-sentigraph-pre-sale-has-started-71a5ddb9e218  Let me know if you need any help or assistance with Sentigraph details. Meanwhile, we are encouraged by your interest in Sentigraph.  Thanks,  Tboy

Author: johnleema
Title: ⚡ [ANN] SENTIGRAPH.IO ⚡ ⭐ Improving Future Events Based on Emotion Data ⭐
Body: Sentigraph is a system that provides predictive insights aimed at improving future events based on emotion data obtained by analyzing users’ reactions in a given event leveraging Artificial Intelligence and blockchain.
